import React from 'react'
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'

const Navigation = () => {
  return (
    <nav className='w-[40%] mt-16 flex justify-around align-middle
    border border-cyan rounded-lg
    '>
        <NavLink to={"/"} className="w-full text-base text-center font-nunito m-2.5 bg-gray-200 text-gray-100
        hover:text-cyan active:bg-cyan active:text-gray-300 border-0 cursor-pointer rounded-md
        ">
            Crypto
        </NavLink>
    </nav>
  )
}

export default Navigation
